creator: Letitia Elizabeth Landon
description: LibriVox volunteers bring you 10 recordings of The Power of Words by Letitia Elizabeth Landon. This was the Weekly Poetry project for February 23, 2014. Read in English by Claudia Salto; CaprishaPage; David Lawrence; Elise C. Boucher; Jason Mills; Julia Niedermaier; John Sercel; Lee Ann Howlett; Leonard Wilson and ravenotation. Letitia Elizabeth Landon was an English poet and novelist, better known by her initials L. E. L. For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
